|gf_REY=22|ga_REY=62\n\n|col_P=green1|text_P=Promoted to [[2008 \u00darvalsdeild]]\n|result1=P|result2=P|result3=P\n|col_R=red1|text_R=Relegated to [[2008 2. deild karla|2008 2. deild]]\n|result12=R\n\n|note_res_P=R\n|note_res_R=Due to the [[\u00darvalsdeild]] expanding to 12 teams, 3 teams were promoted and only 1 relegated from [[1. deild karla (football)|1. deild karla]] in order to keep 12 teams in the league.\n\n|update=complete|source=[http://www.rsssf.com/tablesi/ijs07.html rsssf.com]\n}}\n\n==Top scorers==\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|-\n!Scorer\n!Goals\n!Team\n|-\n|{{flagicon|ISL}} [[Hj\u00f6rtur Hjartarson]]\n|align=center|18\n|[[Knattspyrnuf\u00e9lagi\u00f0 \u00der\u00f3ttur|\u00der\u00f3ttur R.]]\n|-\n|{{flagicon|ISL}} [[Atli Vi\u00f0ar Bj\u00f6rnsson]]\n|align=center|14\n|[[Ungmennaf\u00e9lagi\u00f0 Fj\u00f6lnir|Fj\u00f6lnir]]\n|-\n|{{flagicon|ISL}} [[Gunnar M\u00e1r Gu\u00f0mundsson]]\n|align=center|12\n|[[Ungmennaf\u00e9lagi\u00f0 Fj\u00f6lnir|Fj\u00f6lnir]]\n|-\n|{{flagicon|ISL}} [[Gu\u00f0j\u00f3n Baldvinsson]]\n|align=center|12\n|[[Stjarnan]]\n|-\n|{{flagicon|ISL}} [[Hreinn Hringsson]]\n|align=center|11\n|[[\u00de\u00f3r Akureyri|\u00de\u00f3r A.]]\n|-\n|{{flagicon|DEN}} [[Jakob Spangsberg Jensen]]\n|align=center|10\n|[[Leiknir Reykjav\u00edk|Leiknir R.]]\n|-\n|{{flagicon|ISL}} [[Adolf Sveinsson]]\n|align=center|10\n|[[Knattspyrnuf\u00e9lagi\u00f0 \u00der\u00f3ttur|\u00der\u00f3ttur R.]]\n|-\n|{{flagicon|ISL}} [[T\u00f3mas Leifsson]]\n|align=center|9\n|[[Ungmennaf\u00e9lagi\u00f0 Fj\u00f6lnir|Fj\u00f6lnir]]\n|-\n|{{flagicon|SCO}} [[Paul McShane (Scottish footballer)|Paul McShane]]\n|align=center|9\n|[[Knattspyrnudeild UMFG|Grindav\u00edk]]\n|-\n|{{flagicon|ENG}} [[Ian David Jeffs]]\n|align=center|9\n|[[\u00cd\u00fer\u00f3ttabandalag Vestmannaeyja|\u00cdBV]]\n|-\n|{{flagicon|ISL}} [[Andri Steinn Birgisson]]\n|align=center|8\n|[[Knattspyrnudeild UMFG|Grindav\u00edk]]\n|-\n|{{flagicon|SCO}} [[Scott McKenna Ramsey|Scott Ramsey]]\n|align=center|8\n|[[Knattspyrnudeild UMFG|Grindav\u00edk]]\n|-\n|{{flagicon|ISL}} [[Atli Heimisson]]\n|align=center|8\n|[[\u00cd\u00fer\u00f3ttabandalag Vestmannaeyja|\u00cdBV]]\n|-\n|}\n\n==References==\n*[http://www.rsssf.com/tablesi/ijs07.html RSSSF Page]\n\n{{1. deild karla seasons}}\n{{2006\u201307 in European football (UEFA)}}\n{{2007\u201308 in European football (UEFA)}}\n\n[[Category:1. deild karla (football) seasons]]\n[[Category:2006\u201307 in European second tier association football leagues|Iceland]]\n[[Category:2007\u201308 in European second tier association football leagues|Iceland]]\n[[Category:2007 in Icelandic football|2]]\n", "text_old": "The '''2007 season''' of '''[[1. deild karla (football)|1. deild karla]]''' was the 53rd season of second-tier football in [[Iceland]].\n\n==Standings==\n{{fb cl header}}\n|- \n|1||[[Knattspyrnudeild UMFG|Grindav\u00edk]]||22||15||2||5||47||21||+26||47||align=\"center\" rowspan=\"3\"|[[Promoted]] to [[2008 \u00darvalsdeild]]\n|-\n|2||[[Knattspyrnuf\u00e9lagi\u00f0 \u00der\u00f3ttur|\u00der\u00f3ttur R.]]||22||14||5||3||47||24||+23||47\n|-\n|3||[[Ungmennaf\u00e9lagi\u00f0 Fj\u00f6lnir|Fj\u00f6lnir]]||22||14||3||5||61||29||+32||45 \n|-\n|4||[[\u00cd\u00fer\u00f3ttabandalag Vestmannaeyja|\u00cdBV]]||22||13||5||4||42||23||+19||44\n|-\n|5||[[Knattspyrnuf\u00e9lag Fjar\u00f0abygg\u00f0ar|Fjar\u00f0abygg\u00f0]]||22||11||4||7||23||17||+6||37\n|-\n|6||[[Leiknir Reykjav\u00edk|Leiknir R.]]||22||6||7||9||22||27||-5||25\n|-\n|7||[[\u00de\u00f3r Akureyri|\u00de\u00f3r A.]]||22||6||6||10||33||40||-7||24\n|-\n|8||[[Ungmennaf\u00e9lag Njar\u00f0v\u00edkur|Njar\u00f0v\u00edk]]||22||5||8||9||25||32||-7||23\n|- \n|9||[[Stjarnan]]||22||5||5||12||39||44||-5||20\n|- \n|10||[[Ungmennaf\u00e9lagi\u00f0 V\u00edkingur|V\u00edkingur \u00d3.]]||22||5||5||12||22||33||-11||20\n|-\n|11||[[Knattspyrnuf\u00e9lag Akureyrar|KA]]||22||5||4||13||14||45||-31||19\n|- \n|12||[[Reynir Sandger\u00f0i|Reynir S.]]||22||3||7||12||22||62||-40||16 ||align=\"center\" rowspan=\"1\"|[